CS537 Homework Assignment 1 Getting Started: 
Author: Bingyao Huang
Date: 01/09/2016
Language: C++

This code uses OpenGL to draw 1 red triangle, 1 red quadrilateral and 1 red pentagon in a window named "Red Triangle".

Contents:
	source files: red_triangle.cpp, InitShader.cpp
	makefile: Makefile
	library folder: include
	

Usage:	
	make: the default target compiles all the code
	make run: executes the program(s)
	make clean: deletes all the object files and executable files.
	
	

	

